  Maksymilian Arciemowicz, Manfred Schwarb, Marcin Rataj, Ray Satiro, rilysh,
  Romain Geissler, Samuel Henrique, sd0 on hackerone, Sohom Datta,
  Stefan Eissing, Torben Dury, Viktor Szakats
  (27 contributors)

